13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>此篇為各筆記之整理，非原創內容，資料來源可見下方連結與文後參考資料</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"步驟\"><a href=\"#步驟\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"步驟\"></a>步驟</h1><h2 id=\"更新\"><a href=\"#更新\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更新\"></a>更新</h2><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\">\n<code>sudo apt-get update</code>\n</pre>\n\n<pre class=\"language-bash command-line\">\n<code>sudo apt-get upgrade</code>\n</pre>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"安裝-git\"><a href=\"#安裝-git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 git\"></a>安裝 git</h2><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\">\n<code>sudo apt install -y git</code>\n</pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"查看-python-版本\"><a href=\"#查看-python-版本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看 python 版本\"></a>查看 python 版本</h2><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\"\n     data-output=\"2-5\">\n<code>python3\n  Python 3.8.10 (default, Jun 22 2022, 20:18:18)\n  [GCC 9.4.0] on linux\n  Type \"help\", \"copyright\", \"credits\" or \"license\" for more information.\n  >>> exit()</code>\n</pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"安裝-pip3\"><a href=\"#安裝-pip3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 pip3\"></a>安裝 pip3</h2><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\">\n<code>sudo apt install -y python3-pip</code>\n</pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"安裝-flask\"><a href=\"#安裝-flask\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 flask\"></a>安裝 flask</h2><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\">\n<code>pip3 install flask</code>\n</pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"下載-CTFd\"><a href=\"#下載-CTFd\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載 CTFd\"></a>下載 CTFd</h2><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\">\n<code>git clone https://github.com/isislab/CTFd</code>\n</pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"安裝-CTFd-及相依套件\"><a href=\"#安裝-CTFd-及相依套件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 CTFd 及相依套件\"></a>安裝 CTFd 及相依套件</h2><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\">\n<code>cd CTFd</code>\n</pre>\n\n<pre class=\"language-bash command-line\"\n     data-prompt=\"[user@localhost]:~/CTFd $\">\n<code>pip3 install -r requirements.txt</code>\n</pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"執行\"><a href=\"#執行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"執行\"></a>執行</h2><h3 id=\"法一-本地訪問\"><a href=\"#法一-本地訪問\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"法一::本地訪問\"></a>法一::本地訪問</h3><ol>\n<li><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\"\n  data-prompt=\"[user@localhost]:~/CTFd $\">\n<code>python3 serve.python</code>\n</pre></li>\n<li>瀏覽器輸入<code>127.0.0.1:4000</code><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LEUNswh.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"法二-IP-訪問\"><a href=\"#法二-IP-訪問\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"法二::IP 訪問\"></a>法二::IP 訪問</h3><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\"\n     data-prompt=\"[user@localhost]:~/CTFd $\">\n<code>pip3 install gunicorn</code>\n<code>gunicorn --bind 0.0.0.0:8000 -w 20 \"CTFd:create_app()\"</code>\n</pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"遇到問題\"><a href=\"#遇到問題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"遇到問題\"></a>遇到問題</h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Command &#x27;gunicorn&#x27; not found</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"解決\"><a href=\"#解決\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解決\"></a>解決</h4><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\"\n     data-output=\"2-11\">\n<code>pip3 show gunicorn\n  Name: gunicorn\n  Version: 20.1.0\n  Summary: WSGI HTTP Server for UNIX information.\n  Home-page: https://gunicorn.org\n  Author: Benoit Chesneau\n  Author-email: benoitc@e-engura.com\n  License: MIT\n  <mark>Location: /home/hunter/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages</mark>\n  Requires: setuptools\n  Required-by:</code>\n</pre>\n\n<pre class=\"language-bash command-line\"\n     data-output=\"2\">\n<code>ls /home/hunter/.local/\n  <mark>bin</mark> include lib</code>\n</pre>\n\n<pre class=\"language-bash command-line\">\n<code>export PATH=$PATH:$HOME/.local/bin</code>\n</pre>\n\n<pre class=\"language-bash command-line\"\n     data-prompt=\"[user@localhost]:~/CTFd $\">\n<code>gunicorn --bind 0.0.0.0:8000 -w 20 \"CTFd:create_app()\"</code>\n</pre>\n\n<p>瀏覽器輸入<code>[yourIP]:4000</code><br><code>IP</code> 查詢</p>\n<p><pre class=\"language-bash command-line\"\n     data-output=\"2-18\"><br><code>ifconfig<br>  eth0: flags=4163<UP,BROADCAST,RUNNING,MULTICAST>  mtu 1500<br>        inet <mark>172.31.123.234</mark>  netmask 255.255.240.0  broadcast 172.31.127.255<br>        inet6 fe80::215:5dff:fe77:706d  prefixlen 64  scopeid 0x20<link><br>        ether 00:15:5d:77:70:6d  txqueuelen 1000  (Ethernet)<br>        RX packets 64844  bytes 284195303 (284.1 MB)<br>        RX errors 0  dropped 0  overruns 0  frame 0<br>        TX packets 58124  bytes 4043443 (4.0 MB)<br>        TX errors 0  dropped 0 overruns 0  carrier 0  collisions 0</p>\n<p>  lo: flags=73<UP,LOOPBACK,RUNNING>  mtu 65536<br>        inet 127.0.0.1  netmask 255.0.0.0<br>        inet6 ::1  prefixlen 128  scopeid 0x10<host><br>        loop  txqueuelen 1000  (Local Loopback)<br>        RX packets 503  bytes 3713955 (3.7 MB)<br>        RX errors 0  dropped 0  overruns 0  frame 0<br>        TX packets 503  bytes 3713955 (3.7 MB)<br>        TX errors 0  dropped 0 overruns 0  carrier 0  collisions 0&lt;/code&gt;<br>&lt;/pre&gt;<br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W6Wzs7Y.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"參考資料\"><a href=\"#參考資料\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"參考資料\"></a>參考資料</h1><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1sv411B7U4/?vd_source=1470cbaff3e4133d7ce5f3a99f0ef3ab\">【CTFd】教你如何用Ubuntu快速搭建一個屬於自己的CTF靶場</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/29679963/why-gunicorn-command-not-found-with-gunicorn-installed\">why gunicorn command not found with gunicorn installed?</a></li>\n</ul>\n","text":" 此篇為各筆記之整理，非原創內容，資料來源可見下方連結與文後參考資料 步驟更新 sudo apt-get update sudo apt-get upgrade 安裝 git sudo apt install -y git 查看 python 版本 python3 Python ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.1k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"CTF","slug":"CTF","count":1,"path":"api/categories/CTF.json"}],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"to